      <title>HEXO基本操作</title>
      <link href="/2020/02/28/HEXO%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/"/>
      <url>/2020/02/28/HEXO%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li>HEXO基本操作</li><li>HEXO写作标记</li></ul><a id="more"></a><h2 id="HEXO基本操作"><a href="#HEXO基本操作" class="headerlink" title="HEXO基本操作"></a>HEXO基本操作</h2><p><btn><a href="/">创建新文章或页面</a></btn><br><code>$ hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;</code> 默认使用post<br>Hexo 会根据 scaffolds 文件夹内相对应的文件来建立文件。<br>如果不想文章被引擎编译，可以将Front-Matter 中的layout: 设为 false 。<br>Front-matter 是文件最上方以 — 分隔的区域，用于指定个别文件的变量。<br><btn><a href="/">清理生成文件</a></btn><br><code>$ hexo clean</code><br>当有一些页面变动时，需要清理一下，只是增加内容，一般不需要clean。<br><btn><a href="/">生成blog文件</a></btn><br><code>$ hexo g</code><br>内容完成后，进行生成。<br><btn><a href="/">部署文件到服务器</a></btn><br><code>$ hexo d</code><br>将生成的文件部署到服务器上。也就是说，必须要有生成文件才能部署。<br><btn><a href="/">开启本地服务</a></btn><br><code>$ hexo s</code><br>开启后，在浏览器内输入localhost:4000即可查看blog。前提也是有生成文件。</p><h2 id="HEXO写作标记"><a href="#HEXO写作标记" class="headerlink" title="HEXO写作标记"></a>HEXO写作标记</h2><p>我是对VOLANTIS进行的配置，写作其他内容可以<a href="https://volantis.js.org/tag-plugins/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">参考该地址</a>。<br>HEXO基本上参考Markdown语法，简单粘贴一下。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"># Heading 1</span><br><span class="line">## Heading 2</span><br><span class="line">### Heading 3</span><br><span class="line">#### Heading 4</span><br><span class="line">##### Heading 5</span><br><span class="line">###### Heading 6</span><br><span class="line">- Red</span><br><span class="line">+ Green</span><br><span class="line">* Blue</span><br><span class="line">1. Red</span><br><span class="line">2. Green</span><br><span class="line">3. Blue</span><br><span class="line">- [ ] Milk</span><br><span class="line">- [x] Bread</span><br><span class="line">&gt; First level, first paragraph. 引文</span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&gt; &gt; Second level, first paragraph.</span><br><span class="line">&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&gt; First level, second paragraph.</span><br><span class="line">*** 分割线</span><br><span class="line">--- 分割线</span><br><span class="line">+++ 分页线</span><br><span class="line">This is an [inline link](https:&#x2F;&#x2F;example.com).</span><br><span class="line">This is a [reference link][id].</span><br><span class="line">[id]: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;example.com</span><br><span class="line">**bold**</span><br><span class="line">__bold__</span><br><span class="line">*italic*</span><br><span class="line">_italic_</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
