      <title>HEXO主题设置概述</title>
      <link href="/2020/02/28/HEXO%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0/"/>
      <url>/2020/02/28/HEXO%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li>HEXO默认设置</li><li>HEXO主题设置</li><li>HEXO页面配置</li></ul><a id="more"></a><h2 id="HEXO默认设置"><a href="#HEXO默认设置" class="headerlink" title="HEXO默认设置"></a>HEXO默认设置</h2><p>只提及常用设置，其他设置可以参考HEXO网站<br>打开主目录下的<code>_config.yml</code>文件进行网站配置</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">##Site</span><br><span class="line">title: 网站标题</span><br><span class="line">subtitle: 网站副标题</span><br><span class="line">description: 网站描述</span><br><span class="line">keywords: 网站的关键词。使用半角逗号 , 分隔多个关键词。</span><br><span class="line">author: 您的名字</span><br><span class="line">language: 网站使用的语言  zh-CN</span><br><span class="line">timezone: 网站时区  Asia&#x2F;Shanghai </span><br><span class="line">favicon: 网页标签图标</span><br><span class="line">avatar: 作者头像</span><br><span class="line">##Extensions</span><br><span class="line">theme: 主题名称</span><br><span class="line">copyright: &#39;Copyright © 2020 Bigger Qin&#39; 版权信息</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="HEXO主题设置"><a href="#HEXO主题设置" class="headerlink" title="HEXO主题设置"></a>HEXO主题设置</h2><p>打开<code>themes\主题目录\_config.yml</code>进行主题配置<br>一般开发者都对文件进行了非常好的标注，遵循标注的内容，即可进行很优秀的配置。资源库说明见<a href="https://qpmcool.github.io/2020/02/25/HEXO%E5%85%A5%E5%9D%91%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HEXO入坑指南</a><br>打开<code>themes\主题目录\languages\**.yml</code>进行语言和部分显示信息的配置（例如版权，协议等），部分需要配合css文件进行修改，可忽略。</p><h3 id="封面设置"><a href="#封面设置" class="headerlink" title="封面设置"></a>封面设置</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">features:</span>  <span class="comment"># 封面菜单</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span>  <span class="comment"># 菜单名称 </span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">icon:</span>  <span class="comment"># 菜单图标</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">url:</span>   <span class="comment"># 菜单链接</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>封面菜单为首页主菜单，必要时，可以做成多级的。</p><h3 id="导航栏设置"><a href="#导航栏设置" class="headerlink" title="导航栏设置"></a>导航栏设置</h3><p>菜单链接，需要对应的文件支持，如果source文件夹下没有对应的文件，需要新建。<br>终端  <code>hexo new page 对应目录链接</code><br>完成后，可以进行装饰，支持html5的标签。</p><h2 id="HEXO页面配置"><a href="#HEXO页面配置" class="headerlink" title="HEXO页面配置"></a>HEXO页面配置</h2><p>Blog页面各种链接可能无法使用，需要进行配置生成。<br>独立页面都需要手动创建md文件或用上面介绍的命令生成。<br>通常布局模板有</p><table><thead><tr><th>取值</th><th>含义</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>page</td><td>独立页面</td></tr><tr><td>post</td><td>文章页面</td></tr><tr><td>category</td><td>分类页面</td></tr><tr><td>tag</td><td>标签页面</td></tr><tr><td>links</td><td>友链页面</td></tr><tr><td>list</td><td>列表页面</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="关于页面"><a href="#关于页面" class="headerlink" title="关于页面"></a>关于页面</h3><p>手动创建文件：source/about/index.md</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">layout: page</span><br><span class="line">title: 关于</span><br><span class="line">meta:</span><br><span class="line">  header: []</span><br><span class="line">  footer: []</span><br><span class="line">sidebar: []</span><br><span class="line">valine:</span><br><span class="line">  placeholder: 有什么想对我说的呢？</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">下面写关于自己的内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="分类页面"><a href="#分类页面" class="headerlink" title="分类页面"></a>分类页面</h3><p>手动创建文件：source/categories/index.md</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">layout: category</span><br><span class="line">index: true</span><br><span class="line">title: 所有分类</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure> <h3 id="标签页面"><a href="#标签页面" class="headerlink" title="标签页面"></a>标签页面</h3><p>手动创建文件：source/tags/index.md</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">layout: tag</span><br><span class="line">index: true</span><br><span class="line">title: 所有标签</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="友链页面"><a href="#友链页面" class="headerlink" title="友链页面"></a>友链页面</h3><p>手动创建文件：source/friends/index.md</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">layout: links     # 必须</span><br><span class="line">title: 我的朋友们   # 可选，这是友链页的标题</span><br><span class="line">links:</span><br><span class="line">  - group: 技术大佬</span><br><span class="line">    icon: fas fa-user-tie</span><br><span class="line">    items:</span><br><span class="line">    - name:     # 博客名</span><br><span class="line">      avatar:   # 头像链接</span><br><span class="line">      url:      # 博客链接</span><br><span class="line">      backgroundColor: &#39;#3E74C9&#39; # 卡片背景颜色</span><br><span class="line">      textColor: &#39;#fff&#39;  # 卡片文字颜色</span><br><span class="line">      tags:     # 标签</span><br><span class="line">      - 标签1</span><br><span class="line">      - 标签2</span><br><span class="line">  - group: 分组2</span><br><span class="line">    icon: fas fa-user-tie</span><br><span class="line">    items:</span><br><span class="line">    - name:     # 博客名</span><br><span class="line">      avatar:   # 头像链接</span><br><span class="line">      url:      # 博客链接</span><br><span class="line">      backgroundColor: &#39;#3E74C9&#39; # 卡片背景颜色</span><br><span class="line">      textColor: &#39;#fff&#39;  # 卡片文字颜色</span><br><span class="line">      tags:     # 标签</span><br><span class="line">      - 标签1</span><br><span class="line">      - 标签2</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">这里可以写友链页面下方的文字备注，例如自己的友链规范、示例等。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="404页面"><a href="#404页面" class="headerlink" title="404页面"></a>404页面</h3><p>手动创建文件：source/404.md</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">layout: page</span><br><span class="line">title: 404 Not Found</span><br><span class="line">body: [article, comments]</span><br><span class="line">meta:</span><br><span class="line">  header: []</span><br><span class="line">  footer: []</span><br><span class="line">sidebar: []</span><br><span class="line">valine:</span><br><span class="line">  path: &#x2F;404.html</span><br><span class="line">  placeholder: 请留言告诉我您要访问哪个页面找不到了</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;center&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;h1 style&#x3D;&#39;border-bottom: none;font-size:64px;margin-top:.5em&#39;&gt;404&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;b&gt;很抱歉，您访问的页面不存在&lt;&#x2F;b&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">可能是输入地址有误或该地址已被删除</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;center&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
